long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Speed Racers is a fun racing game where we try to progress and win the races by overcoming complex bends on a track.
There are different tracks in the game. We are on the move with a car on these tracks. We progress by overcoming the problematic bends. Encounter as we move, and we win the races by leaving the competitors behind. By winning the races, we face new opponents. We have the opportunity to continue this adventure for long periods. Speed Racers has emerged as a racing game that has prepared us, car game lovers, as it is fun and challenging.
